Description:
Luxury Living in Meridian Estate!
This beautiful near-new home in Dandenong's Meridian Estate and offers you generous space, quality fittings and great access to amenities. Located on a quiet street with beautiful and contemporary appeal, this single-level 5-year
old home provides you with modernity that accompanies newer builds. Outside, a double lock up garage with remote access keeps your vehicles under shelter and comes with a direct internal entrance.
Step inside to the formal lounge which is great for entertainment or useful as a home office or study; adjoining master bedroom with ensuite and walk-in robe is generous in space. Aspiring Masterchefs will love the well designed and equipped kitchen with island bench, integrated 900 mm gas cook top and oven with accompanying rangehood, dishwasher, stone bench tops, well-sized pantry and glass splashbacks.
The other bedrooms are generous in space, with plenty of storage throughout with built in robes in all bedroom and the central bathroom and separate toilet is ideally placed adjacent to the bedrooms. The rumpus is multi-function in its uses and can double up as a kids playroom, theatre room or even as a 5th bedroom. A covered entertainment deck adjacent to the dining hall is perfect for summer entertaining and rear garden is right-sized for enjoyment and easy maintenance. Central gas ducted heating and evaporative cooling takes care of your winter and summer needs.
This home is one of the best that you will see in the Dandenong area and fits the needs of any family who loves to entertain. Make sure that you arrange to inspect before it is too late!

Description:
King Of The World!
Unique in so many ways, this substantial double story home is ideal for the growing family and has a sensational roof top entertaining area with amazing 360 degree views of Dandenong and surrounding areas that needs to be seen to be believed!
Downstairs – Comprises of a formal lounge and family/meals area overlooking the hostess kitchen with granite benchtops, stainless steel appliances and dishwasher. The convenience of two bedrooms with built in robes, bathroom with granite benchtop, a study nook, under stairs storage, laundry and toilet.
Upstairs – Comprises of another living area or theatre room, three other bedrooms with built in robes, a study or 6th bedroom, bathroom with granite benchtop, toilet and balcony.
Rooftop – A huge entertaining area with wrap around balcony and an amazing place to relax or just enjoy the sunshine while sitting on top of your unique home.
- Outside you will find an oversized double garage and spacious backyard with plenty of room for the kids or family pets. Unlike any other homes on the market, this fantastic family home is constructed of double brick exterior and brick interior walls, concrete slab floor, suspended concrete ceiling and roof, opening up potential possibilities to extend further living areas on the third floor! Other inclusions are security window shutters, alarm and brick front fence with gates.
Centrally located close to public transport, Public & Private Hospitals, schools, parkland, Dandenong Market and Dandenong Plaza, this is an amazing and affordable opportunity to purchase a large family home in a central location with huge potential to add further value all while adding your own personal touches and finishes to make it your own. Owner will consider all reasonable offers, so make your enquiry today!
“Selling? You’ll be SOLD with our $8,800 Success Fee“

Description:
Smart style and super spacious!
Young, contemporary and so spacious throughout, this 3 bedroom family home offers the best things for an easy lifestyle. It's low maintenance living without sacrificing space or outdoor entertaining.
Large fully tiled living area with split system heating & cooling with extensive glass overlooking courtyard garden. Modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, glass splashback and stone bench tops.
The smart design allows for split living with the main bedroom downstairs with robes and full ensuite bathroom. Upstairs offers a second carpeted lounging area with cooling and an extra 2 large bedrooms both with robes. The upstairs full bathroom is well positioned between the bedrooms.
Step through sliding glass doors from the living area onto the deck looking over the private rear garden. An oversized garage with remote door and rear access offers off street parking for 2 cars.
Positioned in popular Metro Village Dandenong within walking distance to the city centre and Dandenong station plus easy access to Monash, Eastlink plus bike and walking tracks.

Description:
Central Living at its Finest!
Plant yourself in the epicentre of exotic and bustling Dandenong in this 3 bedroom home just a short walk from Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, and every amenity imaginable.
Whether you're looking to secure a comfortable future for your family, a first home buyer, developer or an astute investor seeking to grow your portfolio, don't miss the opportunity to take a look inside this immaculate residence on a magnificent 650sqm allotment.
Entertainers will revel in the massive space of the open plan kitchen, 3m high ceilings, dining and living area that will be the envy of friends and family members. The high end chef's kitchen with enormous wrap around bench, double SS sink, huge pantry, decorative splash back tiles and abundance of natural light is ideal for whipping up gastronomical delights.
Three bedrooms tucked in rear offer added privacy, two with BIRs, the master suite with huge walk-in robe and ensuite.
Take the entertainment outside to a large and grassy north-facing yard perfect for active kids and pets, and an enormous undercover al fresco area for every imaginable outdoor soiree. With many features including solar panels, ducted heating, security shutters, ducted vacuum and evaporative cooling, this provides the most comfortable of lifestyles.
Double car garage, garden shed, bungalow/man cave, large laundry and heaps of closet space complete this flawless package in a high density residential growth zone.

Description:
Family Home in the Heart of Meridian Estate!
This quality-built family home is approximately only 6 years young, modern and well-planned within a popular and convenient neighbourhood with easy access to parks, trails, EastLink, public transport and the vibrant Dandenong dining and shopping district.
This home is striking from the first impression, with low maintenance gardens and a modern façade. The build is inclusive of a double garage with internal access and heating and cooling for all year round comfort. Upon entry is a study and formal lounge, rumpus room, large laundry and powder room. Next, head into the open living, dining and kitchen areas that further opens to the entertaining alfresco for family and friends to enjoy.
Upstairs is sure to impress with the expansive master bedroom, inclusive of extensive ensuite with vanity, dressing room and private balcony. Alongside the master is an activity room, ideal for the family, plus three bedrooms as well as a shared family bathroom with separate toilet.
This home is ideal and one to impress, it will cater for all members of the family. The low maintenance gardens also give the children a place to play or the adults room to entertain.
Do not hesitate on this prime double storey and enquire for an inspection today.

- 5 Bedrooms + Study Room

- Land Size: 455 sqm (approx.)

Brand New and Ready To Move In!
Looking for a brand-new home with completion not too far away? Well look no further as we present to you this modern three-bedroom family home located in a prime location of Dandenong; close to public transport, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong North primary school, Dandenong High school, parks and Dandenong Market.
Upon entry you are greeted with the light filled lounge area that is overlooked by the kitchen with plenty of cupboard space and a dishwasher. Nearby is the meals area where the family can enjoy a delicious home cooked dinner.
Make your way upstairs to the open plan retreat area that grants you access to the balcony. Branching off this living space are the three bedrooms; the master with an en-suite and walk in robe whilst the remaining two bedrooms comprise of built in robes and are central to the main bathroom.
Further comforts include a powder room, split system heating and cooling, high ceilings, a 2000L water tank, landscaping, a single garage and semi-covered carport and much more.
With everything brand new and done for you, all you have to do is move straight in.
